Richard asked:


 can I get new keys for my 73?  mine were stolen.

 can I do it with just part number off the cylinder in the ignition ?

 ----------------------------------------------------------------------

IF you had just one key for all the locks, then yes you can get a new key cut to your code.

Remove one of the front door handles and get the code off the paddle.
It will resemble 12R345
http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/306807.jpg

